{"tid":1884585,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科技部：康復者血漿療法安全有效，呼籲治愈患者獻出血漿","createTime":"2020-02-17T16:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T17:37:25.000Z","uid":85180,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"caef86144301b7bc7ac4c47ebdaf987f5916a3df","tid":1884585,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:33:39.000Z","msg":"科技部：康復者血漿療法安全有效，呼籲治愈患者獻出血漿<br />\n<br />\n新京報快訊（記者許雯）國務院聯防聯控機制2月17日舉行新聞發布會。科技部生物中心副主任孫燕榮介紹，康復者血漿治療是古老而又創新的急救措施之一。現在接受血漿治療的患者中1位已出院，1位可以下地行走，其他患者正在恢復。科技部將及時跟踪，進行風險評估，目前認為採集恢復期患者血漿用於患者治療安全有效，可以採納。她呼籲，開展&ldquo;千人獻漿救千人&rdquo;的活動，希望康復者獻出血漿，讓生命接續。<br />\n<br />\n新京報記者許雯<br />\n<br />\n編輯劉夢婕"},{"pid":"f283cded7ae4eee65a48993b7672be95a25247d2","tid":1884585,"uid":67487,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"會唔會染到其他病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5f29a2287c5d320ffa463d39d20fb3dd660039","tid":1884585,"uid":261332,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"千人aids 計劃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20ce40653e8b76afd2f973cccdffb8daa17f701","tid":1884585,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"我懷疑係想趁機 叫人去捐血<br />\n再攞去賣<br />\n<br />\n平時支國捐血應該係有錢攞"},{"pid":"d08b801b29ff7b1ba274a4ed9c645ea8819a869b","tid":1884585,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:38:27.000Z","msg":"蟈蛺真強大，滯留匪區的港民可以放心鳥"},{"pid":"b5b8973407175251cc2feb91d2d4951b77ad63c9","tid":1884585,"uid":292497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:42:24.000Z","msg":"獻出你既心臟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537410d8359cf3e922b2cbfde2117ba5adf75046","tid":1884585,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a5f29a2287c5d320ffa463d39d20fb3dd660039","tid":1884585,"uid":261332,"like":6,"dislik